\newlabel{fig:route_heatmap}{{7}{23}{Route classification heatmap. Lot's O' Nuts and Wicked Choccy's are Congested across all regions; The Other Factory is Efficient across all regions; Secret Factory is Moderate across all regions; Sugar Shack is highly inconsistent --- Optimised in Gulf, Bottleneck in Atlantic, Interior, and Pacific}{figure.caption.16}{}}
