\newlabel{fig:route_bubble}{{8}{23}{Route cluster bubble chart. Sugar Shack--Pacific sits in the upper portion (highest lead time despite moderate distance). Sugar Shack--Gulf is an anomalous low outlier (fast despite 1,321 miles). Congested routes (Lot's O' Nuts and Wicked Choccy's, large bubbles) cluster around 1,310--1,330 days regardless of distance, confirming that their elevated lead times are volume-driven rather than geography-driven}{figure.caption.17}{}}
